snippet.title: 1920x1080 Real Stop AppPreview EN
snippet.description:
You may know it as Stop; Petit Bac; Stadt, Land, Fluss; or any other number of names depending on where you were born. All we know is that it's the most fun you can have while pretending to do something else.

Download Stop for free on the App Store today at https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/stop-... 

And 

On the Google Play store at 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fanatee.stop&hl
